      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POP SAID YES (8) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 19.55. Draws out wide but has the ability and in winning form. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Great chance again. LOOKING FANCY (7) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 366m (19.95). Bold showing expected. FARMOR RELIEF (3) showed good pace from out wide and was prominent throughout before fading out of it when 7th at this track in a Free For All. Solid record here at the distance winning 11 races. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Bold showing expected. WEATHER REPORT (4) warrants respect with the drop in distance.",
